{"iti86:0.1":"Itivuttaka 86 ","iti86:0.2":"Tikanipata ","iti86:0.3":"Catutthavagga ","iti86:0.4":"Dhammanudhammapatipannasutta ","iti86:1.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata vuttamarahatati me sutam: ","iti86:2.1":"“Dhammanudhammapatipannassa bhikkhuno ayamanudhammo hoti veyyakaranaya—","iti86:2.2":"dhammanudhammapatipannoyanti bhasamano dhammanneva bhasati no adhammam, vitakkayamano va dhammavitakkanneva vitakketi no adhammavitakkam, tadubhayam va pana abhinivejjetva upekkhako viharati sato sampajano”ti. ","iti86:2.3":"Etamattham bhagava avoca. ","iti86:2.4":"Tatthetam iti vuccati: ","iti86:3.1":"“Dhammaramo dhammarato, ","iti86:3.2":"dhammam anuvicintayam; ","iti86:3.3":"Dhammam anussaram bhikkhu, ","iti86:3.4":"saddhamma na parihayati. ","iti86:4.1":"Caram va yadi va tittham, ","iti86:4.2":"nisinno uda va sayam; ","iti86:4.3":"Ajjhattam samayam cittam, ","iti86:4.4":"santimevadhigacchati”ti. ","iti86:5.1":"Ayampi attho vutto bhagavata, iti me sutanti. ","iti86:5.2":"Sattamam. "}